", 1)).isNotNull();\n        assertThat(scope.getFunction(\"paths\", 0)).isNotNull();\n\n        JsonQuery query = JsonQuery.compile(\"map(. + 1)\", Versions.JQ_1_6);\n        List<JsonNode> outputs = new ArrayList<>();\n        query.apply(scope, mapper.readTree(\"[1, 2, 3]\"), outputs::add);\n\n        assertThat(outputs).containsExactly(mapper.readTree(\"[2, 3, 4]\"));\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782594514912}, {"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_AIQuVkmhEHfcgEZzSvI5Qx8A|fc_0ca75e4f858dc8c6016a403bd2aff081978cfef412b652a748", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "metadata/net.thisptr/jackson-jq/index.json:5:    \"source-code-url\" : \"https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/net/thisptr/jackson-jq/$version$/jackson-jq-$version$-sources.jar\",\nmetadata/net.thisptr/jackson-jq/index.json:6:    \"repository-url\" : \"https://github.com/eiiches/jackson-jq\",\nmetadata/net.thisptr/jackson-jq/index.json:7:    \"test-code-url\" : \"https://github.com/eiiches/jackson-jq/tree/$version$/jackson-jq/src/test\",\nmetadata/net.thisptr/jackson-jq/index.json:8:    \"documentation-url\" : \"https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/net/thisptr/jackson-jq/$version$/jackson-jq-$version$-javadoc.jar\",\nmetadata/net.thisptr/jackson-jq/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"jackson-jq is a pure Java implementation of the jq JSON query language for Jackson's JSON tree model. It lets JVM applications parse and execute jq filters against Jackson JsonNode values, including built-in functions and optional command-line tooling.\",\nmetadata/net.thisptr/jackson-jq/index.json:14:      \"net.thisptr.jackson.jq\"\nmetadata/net.thisptr/jackson-jq/1.6.2/reachability-metadata.json:5:        \"typeReached\": \"net.thisptr.jackson.jq.BuiltinFunctionLoader\"\nmetadata/net.thisptr/jackson-jq/1.6.2/reachability-metadata.json:11:        \"typeReached\": \"net.thisptr.jackson.jq.Scope\"\nmetadata/net.thisptr/jackson-jq/1.6.2/reachability-metadata.json:17:        \"typeReached\": 