4;last&#44;nth&#40;n&#41;)                                                                                                                                                                                           | ○          |\n| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull; [`foreach`](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#foreach)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     | ○          |\n| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull; [Recursion](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#Recursion)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   | ○          |\n| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull; [Generators and iterators](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#Generatorsanditerators)                                                                                                                                                                                                       | ○          |\n| [Math](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#Math)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            | △          |\n| [I&#47;O](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#I&#47;O)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      | N/A        |\n| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull; [`input`](https://stedolan.github