            | ○<sup>*2</sup> |\n| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull; [`?` operator](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#&#63;operator)                                                                                                                                                                                                                            | ○          |\n| [Regular expressions &#40;PCRE&#41;](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#Regularexpressions&#40;PCRE&#41;)                                                                                                                                                                                                                  | ○          |\n| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull; [`test(val)`, `test(regex; flags)`](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#test&#40;val&#41;&#44;test&#40;regex&#59;flags&#41;)                                                                                                                                                                 | ○          |\n| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull; [`match(val)`, `match(regex; flags)`](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#match&#40;val&#41;&#44;match&#40;regex&#59;flags&#41;)                                                                                                                                                             | ○          |\n| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull; [`capture(val)`, `capture(regex; flags)`](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#capture&#40;val&#41;&#44;capture&#40;regex&#59;flags&#41;)                                                                                                                                                     | ○          |\n| &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull; [`scan(regex)`, `scan(regex; flags)`](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/manual/v1.5/#scan&#40;regex&#41;&#44;scan&#40;regex&#59;flags&#41;)                                                                                               